<ChannelTradeLayout
  title="AI Instagram DMs for UK Shopfitters | Rapid Receptionist"
  description={`AI Instagram DMs for UK shopfitting companies. Converts followers inspired by venue transformation reels into retail, restaurant, and salon fit-out consultations. Add-on at £${pricing.addOn.price}/month.`}
  canonicalUrl="/shopfitters/ai-instagram-dms/"
  channelName="AI Instagram DMs"
  tradeName="Shopfitter"
  tradeNamePlural="Shopfitters"
  tradeSlug="shopfitters"
  headline="AI Instagram DMs for UK Shopfitting Companies"
  accentWord="Shopfitting"
  subhead="Your latest reel is a sixty-second time-lapse of a cocktail bar fit-out in Jericho — starting with a bare shell, showing the bespoke herringbone parquet floor being laid, the copper-topped bar counter being positioned, the back-bar shelving with integrated LED uplighting being installed, and ending with the final reveal: dim amber lighting, leather bar stools, and a wall of handwritten cocktail menus in illuminated brass frames. Seventy thousand views. A bar operator in Cowley Road DMs: 'Absolutely stunning. We are launching a new cocktail concept and want this exact level of detail. Can you come and look at our unit?' You are on site fitting a retail cash desk in a boutique. Without AI DMs, the message waits. With it, the operator shares his unit address and concept brief, and your lead is captured."
  scenario="It is 1am on a Saturday. A chef in Oxford has just finished service at the restaurant where he works. He has been planning his own place for two years and has finally secured the lease on a 1,800-square-foot unit in a Victorian building on St Clements. He has been browsing Instagram for shopfitters who understand hospitality — and finds your account. Your portfolio shows exactly what he wants: open kitchens with pass counters, exposed services as a design feature, and bespoke joinery that feels both industrial and refined. He DMs: 'Chef looking to open my own restaurant in OX4. Large unit, 1,800sqft, Victorian building. Want an open kitchen with a pass counter overlooking the dining room, exposed ductwork as a feature, banquette seating for 80 covers, and a small cocktail bar near the entrance. Budget is £150k for the fit-out. I have a concept deck I can send. Interested?' Without AI Instagram DMs, you see the DM Saturday afternoon. He contacted two other shopfitters; one responded at 8am with congratulations and a request for the concept deck. With AI DMs, the reply arrives at 1:01am: 'Congratulations on the new restaurant — hospitality fit-outs with open kitchens and exposed services are among our favourite projects. We would love to see the concept deck. Could you share it along with the unit address? One of our team will call you on Monday to discuss the scope and arrange a site walkthrough.' He uploads the concept deck. Saturday at 10am you open the lead: chef-owner restaurant, 1,800sqft Victorian, OX4, open kitchen with pass counter, exposed ductwork, 80-cover banquette, cocktail bar, £150k budget, concept deck attached. You call Monday at 9am."
  benefits={benefits}
  faqs={faqs}
  channelPageUrl="/construction-trades/ai-instagram-dms/"
  tradePageUrl="/shopfitters/ai-receptionist/"
  ctaHeadline="Turn Cocktail Bar Reels into Six-Figure Fit-Out Consultations"
  ctaSubhead={`A copper-topped bar counter reel earns seventy thousand views. AI Instagram DMs converts every operator enquiry into a lead with concept, budget, and unit photos. Add-on at £${pricing.addOn.price}/month.`}
